---
name: print-export
type: Agent Requested
description: Génère les services d’exportation PDF et Excel conformes aux normes World Taekwondo (P01 à P18, planning, certificats).
---

When invoked, perform the following:

- Create export service in /services/printService.ts
- Use jsPDF to generate:
    - Match sheets (P01)
    - Referee sheets (P02)
    - Result reports (P18)
    - Certificates (participant, winner, referee)
    - Accreditation and badges
- Use ExcelJS to generate:
    - Planning par aire et session
    - Liste des pesées
    - Brackets et poules

- Use Zod for input validation
- Endpoints (in /routes/print.ts):
    - GET /print/match/:id (P01)
    - GET /print/event/:id (XLSX match plan)
    - GET /print/certificate/participant/:id
    - GET /print/certificate/winner/:id
    - GET /print/badge/:id

- Store generated files in /exports or return as binary
- Include layout templates from /templates/ if needed
- Support languages: EN / FR

Structure:
- routes/print.ts
- services/printService.ts
- dto/print.dto.ts
- templates/p01.html, p02.html...
- exports/{pdf|xlsx}/...

Ensure output is aligned with official WT format and FFTDA usage.